          "correct": "c",
          "difficulty": "easy",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "Law of exponents: when multiplying same bases, add the powers. aᵐ × aⁿ = aᵐ⁺ⁿ."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch12_A_003",
          "text": "The value of (3/4)⁻² is:",
